":80565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f915858a20a2c2e8eb2c9cbb2e30871b263806a","tid":2370732,"uid":250673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f11f80870a2eb4148898dd7eba521e14acfc93d5","tid":2370732,"uid":80565,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"日籍但唔識日文都比較罕見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常掉番轉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"出世幾個月之後就已經嚟咗香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:18:24.000Z","msg":"樓主真名係日本名？定跟香港名？"},{"pid":"50453109b5d57b31667ed04c74225accbc17c9c0","tid":2370732,"uid":76263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:18:51.000Z","msg":"如果你真係想係日本試下做野但又唔知自己適唔適應到既話，日本有一個program 叫「JET program」, 呢個program 其中一part係政府請外國人黎日本教英文為主（好似都有得教其他外語），個program 為期一年，可以續兩次total 教三年<br />\n<br />\n我自己住緊係大阪但我都會想搵個生活節奏更慢既城市，但我又唔想去到d一個鐘得一班車既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我會推薦神户<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生活節奏慢既城市有個唔好處就係工作機會一定會少d 同普遍人工會低d，呢點你都要諗諗<br />\n<br />\n我都係前年grad 左上年黎日本做野，只要你黎到肯放膽同日本人慢慢傾偈既話真係唔使驚日文學唔黎同習慣唔到<br />\n<br />\n生活上我覺得同香港相差唔係大家想像中咁多，所以唔使太擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a3008309d247577eb86481a989ee0ee48f04a6","tid":2370732,"uid":65931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f11f80870a2eb4148898dd7eba521e14acfc93d5","tid":2370732,"uid":80565,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"日籍但唔識日文都比較罕見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常掉番轉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"大把喇<br />\n我自己都識幾個父母其中一個日本人，香港長大"},{"pid":"cc84a79ad910993405f0cc02ca6d44f7370faa49","tid":2370732,"uid":65931,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"樓主你咁後生<br />\n又唔洗公司幫你申請visa 先可以留係日本做野<br />\n其實已經贏左好多人<br />\n趁後生唔好諗咁多試試佢<br />\n唔好令自己後悔<br />\n<br />\n利申：後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23f84cc4d51a0f1fe81631f83ab5340b62c4946","tid":2370732,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76626dab614d20922a20908d90a3be1c457c4385","tid":2370732,"uid":250673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c83e4f66c98ff1c475914348ac07c31c831549a","tid":2370732,"uid":276273,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"你分清乜嘢叫永居、同入籍先諗日本啦！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:52:13.000Z","msg":"日本出生日本國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"去千葉，工事上曾經交手過D漁農水產檢疫公司，<br />\n大都市邊，適合你要求"},{"pid":"e50fc3153474f2760fc021643132f9eeadd62567","tid":2370732,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"做奧運慰安人員"},{"pid":"b5da9c1a9927515bd3db5b8dcc12a5fbdbef2f4d","tid":2370732,"uid":38891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80a3008309d247577eb86481a989ee0ee48f04a6","tid":2370732,"uid":65931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f11f80870a2eb4148898dd7eba521e14acfc93d5","tid":2370732,"uid":80565,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"日籍但唔識日文都比較罕見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常掉番轉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"大把喇<br />\n我自己都識幾個父母其中一個日本人，香港長大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"好正常<br />\n我係泰國人   但係都唔識泰文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac714ff90df1ccb9576a89c9da39b456e905225","tid":2370732,"uid":218413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"438afb0690b690fa0464869d399578b0f4763248","tid":2370732,"uid":250673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"694c11f4ec1213ea83729a79be9e16e74cb365e6","tid":2370732,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT