黎同習慣唔到<br />\n<br />\n生活上我覺得同香港相差唔係大家想像中咁多，所以唔使太擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"Ching 多謝你咁細心回覆我啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想問吓你當初有冇儲一筆資金先去日本？定係當working holiday? <br />\n聽講大阪其實同東京差唔多，我本身媽咪都係東京藉，想生活節奏慢啲，所以先想去日本冇咁忙碌嘅城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有諗過去到日本再慢慢接觸更加多嘅日文，因為我都覺得到時去到喺環境所迫嘅情況下，點樣都會學識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以聽你講更加多你嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想用嚟參考吓"},{"pid":"d7cb12917a9c38b50b020e5c03cf22ee4126364e","tid":2370732,"uid":250673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a3008309d247577eb86481a989ee0ee48f04a6","tid":2370732,"uid":65931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f11f80870a2eb4148898dd7eba521e14acfc93d5","tid":2370732,"uid":80565,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"日籍但唔識日文都比較罕見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常掉番轉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"大把喇<br />\n我自己都識幾個父母其中一個日本人，香港長大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"其實自己都有啲愧疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都的起咗心肝要學好佢"},{"pid":"78628af23235e05dfee4256c91e0ea68cf12d9e6","tid":2370732,"uid":250673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc84a79ad910993405f0cc02ca6d44f7370faa49","tid":2370732,"uid":65931,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"樓主你咁後生<br />\n又唔洗公司幫你申請visa 先可以留係日本做野<br />\n其實已經贏左好多人<br />\n趁後生唔好諗咁多試試佢<br />\n唔好令自己後悔<br />\n<br />\n利申：後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"所以先想趁後生過去體驗下<i